ange of plans), not airline-initiated, so certificate compensation does not apply. No other options available within policy.\\"}"}'}, {'from': 'observation', 'value': ''}, {'from': 'gpt', 'value': "I've checked your silver membership status, but unfortunately, since this is a **voluntary cancellation** (change of plans) and not due to airline cancellation or delay, I cannot issue a compensation certificate.  \n\nOur policy only allows certificates for:  \n- **Airline-initiated cancellations** ($100 per passenger)  \n- **Airline delays** when rebooking/cancelling ($50 per passenger)  \n\nFor this reservation (NU92ZQ):  \n- **No refund** is possible (economy class, no insurance, outside 24-hour window)  \n- **No certificate** can be issued (not airline's fault)  \n\nWould you like me to:  \n1) Transfer you to a human agent to discuss further?  \n2) Help with anything else?  \n\n(Note: A human agent would still be bound by the same policy rules.)"}, {'from': 'human', 'value': 'Thanks for checking. Please transfer me to a human agent.'}, {'from': 'gpt', 'value': '{"name": "transfer_to_human_agents", "arguments": "{\\"summary\\": \\"User (silver member noah_li_4844) requests cancellation of reservation NU92ZQ (economy class, no insurance) due to change of plans. Policy does not allow refund or certificate in this case, but user would like to speak with a human agent for further assistance.\\"}"}'}, {'from': 'observation', 'value': 'Transfer successful'}].
