 per passenger. Unfortunately, I am unable to offer a larger compensation or rebooking directly.\n\nIf you feel that this does not adequately address your situation, I can transfer you to a human agent who may have more flexibility in handling your request. Would you like me to do that?'}, {'from': 'human', 'value': 'Yes, I would like to speak with a human who can possibly provide more assistance. I understand the policies but I still think my case deserves some extra consideration. Please transfer me to a human agent.'}, {'from': 'gpt', 'value': '{"name": "transfer_to_human_agents", "arguments": {"summary": "Chen Taylor, a gold member, experienced a cancellation of the return journey on a round-trip ticket from SEA to DFW on May 8, 2024. The user is seeking additional compensation or assistance beyond the standard $100 certificate per passenger due to the inconvenience caused by the cancellation. Requesting transfer to a human agent for further assistance."}}'}, {'from': 'observation', 'value': 'Transfer successful'}].
