e more detailed assistance or consider your request further.\n\nWould you like me to transfer you to a human agent now?'}, {'from': 'human', 'value': "Yes, please. I'd appreciate if you could transfer me to a human agent. Thank you."}, {'from': 'gpt', 'value': '{"name": "transfer_to_human_agents", "arguments": {"summary": "User with gold status (emma_martin_8571) is requesting to cancel a basic economy round-trip reservation (6SMKV1) despite the strict cancellation policy. The user is hoping for an exception due to their long-standing relationship and gold status."}}'}, {'from': 'observation', 'value': 'Transfer successful'}].
