ed the flight? If not, I will need to transfer you to a human agent for further assistance.'}, {'from': 'human', 'value': "No, the airline hasn't cancelled the flight. It's just a change in our personal plans. Please help me get in touch with a human agent. Thank you."}, {'from': 'gpt', 'value': '{"name": "transfer_to_human_agents", "arguments": {"summary": "User needs to cancel a Basic Economy flight reservation (AFWKA2) due to a change in personal plans. The flight was booked more than 24 hours ago and the user does not have travel insurance. The airline has not cancelled the flight."}}'}, {'from': 'observation', 'value': 'Transfer successful'}].
