 Santos. You do not have travel insurance.\n\nSince you booked this trip more than 24 hours ago and you do not have travel insurance, the cancellation policy for economy flights applies. Unfortunately, economy flights can only be cancelled if travel insurance is purchased and the conditions are met, or if the airline cancels the flight.\n\nGiven these circumstances, I cannot cancel your reservation. If you need further assistance or have any other questions, I can transfer you to a human agent. Would you like to proceed with that?'}, {'from': 'human', 'value': "Let's proceed with it. I understand that usually, cancellations might not be eligible for economy tickets. But I hope a human agent might help me in finding an alternative. Thanks."}, {'from': 'gpt', 'value': '{"name": "transfer_to_human_agents", "arguments": {"summary": "User daiki_lopez_8334 needs to cancel a round trip reservation (2GFKHR) from Newark to Las Vegas due to a change in plans. The user does not have travel insurance and is in economy class. The user hopes a human agent can provide alternatives or assistance."}}'}, {'from': 'observation', 'value': 'Transfer successful'}].
