alue': 'I understand the standard policy, but I was hoping for an exception due to my circumstances. Could you please check with your higher ups or direct me to someone who could assist me with this?'}, {'from': 'gpt', 'value': 'I understand your situation, and I appreciate your understanding of the standard policy. However, I am not able to make exceptions or contact higher-ups directly. The best course of action would be to transfer you to a human agent who can review your case and provide the necessary assistance.\n\nWould you like me to transfer you to a human agent now?'}, {'from': 'human', 'value': 'Yes, please do so. I would appreciate speaking with someone who might be able to assist me further. Thank you.'}, {'from': 'gpt', 'value': '{"name": "transfer_to_human_agents", "arguments": {"summary": "The user (mia_ito_4088) is requesting an exception to cancel their economy flight reservation (7SIK3K) due to personal circumstances, despite missing the 24-hour cancellation window and not having travel insurance. They would like to speak with a human agent for further assistance."}}'}, {'from': 'observation', 'value': 'Transfer successful'}].
