 the key points:\n\n- **Reservation ID:** QUE4VX\n- **User ID:** isabella_lopez_2185\n- **Origin:** SFO\n- **Destination:** MCO\n- **Flight Type:** Round Trip\n- **Cabin Class:** Basic Economy\n- **Flights:**\n  - SFO to BOS (HAT294) on 2024-05-26\n  - BOS to MCO (HAT235) on 2024-05-26\n  - MCO to PHX (HAT161) on 2024-05-27\n  - PHX to SFO (HAT009) on 2024-05-27\n- **Passengers:**\n  - Isabella Lopez (1979-02-10)\n  - Isabella Khan (1952-02-09)\n- **Payment Method:** Credit Card (credit_card_3989253)\n- **Total Amount Paid:** $608\n- **Baggage:** 0 free checked bags\n- **Travel Insurance:** No\n\nSince you are traveling in the basic economy class and do not have travel insurance, the cancellation policy is strict. Cancellations for basic economy flights are only allowed within 24 hours of booking or if the airline cancels the flight. Your reservation was made on 2024-05-14, which is more than 24 hours ago, and there is no indication that the airline has canceled the flight.\n\nGiven these conditions, I am unable to cancel your reservation and provide a refund. However, I understand that this is an emergency, and I will transfer you to a human agent who may be able to assist you further or provide additional options.\n\nWould you like me to proceed with the transfer?'}, {'from': 'human', 'value': "Yes, please. I'd appreciate if you could connect me with a human agent. My situation is urgent, and I need to figure out a solution as soon as possible. Thank you."}, {'from': 'gpt', 'value': '{"name": "transfer_to_human_agents", "arguments": {"summary": "User isabella_lopez_2185 needs to cancel a basic economy reservation (QUE4VX) due to an emergency (mother\'s illness). The user does not have travel insurance and the cancellation is not within the 24-hour window. The user is requesting a human agent for further assistance."}}'}, {'from': 'observation', 'value': 'Transfer successful'}].
