cellation policy is strict. Cancellations are only allowed within 24 hours of booking or if the airline cancels the flight. Unfortunately, it has been more than 24 hours since the booking, and the airline has not cancelled the flight.\n\nTherefore, I am unable to cancel this reservation for you. If you have any further questions or need assistance with other options, please let me know. \n\nWould you like to discuss any other options or need help with something else?'}, {'from': 'human', 'value': 'I understand the rules you mentioned. However, due to the severity of the health issue, I would very much appreciate an opportunity to speak directly to a human agent. Can you arrange this for me?'}, {'from': 'gpt', 'value': '{"name": "transfer_to_human_agents", "arguments": {"summary": "User lei_rossi_3206 needs to cancel economy flight reservation VAAOXJ due to a severe health issue. The user does not have travel insurance and the cancellation is not allowed under the current policy. The user requests to speak to a human agent for further assistance."}}'}, {'from': 'observation', 'value': 'Transfer successful'}].
