or a more satisfactory resolution considering the considerable delay and my status as a gold member. Thank you for your assistance.'}, {'from': 'gpt', 'value': '{"name": "transfer_to_human_agents", "arguments": {"summary": "Mohamed Silva, a gold member with travel insurance, is requesting additional compensation for a 3-hour delay on flight HAT197 from PHL to ORD on May 2nd. He is not satisfied with the standard $50 per passenger certificate and is seeking a higher amount or different type of compensation."}}'}, {'from': 'observation', 'value': 'Transfer successful'}].
